{
  "stem": "20575.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when Hitler came in, maybe the same week, she says Thea, you cannot come and visit anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because my father doesn't let me talk to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father doesn't allow me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For me, this was kind of, you know-- especially her, because she lived very close by.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But otherwise, you know, I was-- I, like I said, there was-- I remember also there were a lot of poor Jewish children in our class.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We-- we used to drink milk, you know, we-- everybody bought milk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody left a little bit milk left in in the bottle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we poured it in the other one so to make a full one again for another child, so that they should have the [INAUDIBLE], because you had to pay for this--",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and didn't get it for free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I loved to go to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- [LAUGHS] I always liked to get all-- all As, always, in-- in class.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, you're a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You really didn't-- didn't know the difference.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, I heard from my parents that-- you know, that they-- from the people that they hung out with, friends who are not Jewish, who actually were illegal Nazis.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they told them, they said, they told them and predicted that this is going to come.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm talking just a-- a month or so before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, because everything was brewing to the point, in Austria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, you-- you should leave here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You should leave here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we said, where should we go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where should you-- can you, like, pick yourself up with two little kids, and where are you going to go?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, but basically, with us, with us children, we-- we had a normal childhood, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
